<section id="faq" class="section" aria-labelledby="faq-title">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section__head section__head--center reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p>
      <h2 id="faq-title">Frequently asked questions</h2>
    </header>

    <div class="faq reveal">
      <details>
        <summary>Is the event open to the public?</summary>
        <p>No. This is an invitation-only business event for selected corporate guests and decision makers.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Who should attend?</summary>
        <p>CEOs, CFOs, founders, entrepreneurs and senior decision makers who manage international operations, payments, liquidity or corporate finance strategy.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Do I need to understand crypto already?</summary>
        <p>No. The event is designed for business leaders who want a practical introduction to digital assets in a corporate context.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Is the derby ticket included?</summary>
        <p>Yes. Confirmed participants will receive a complimentary ticket for Torino vs Juventus. VIP skybox access is limited and subject to availability.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>When will my application be confirmed?</summary>
        <p>The YouHodler team will review applications manually and contact selected guests by email.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Will YouHodler present a new business product?</summary>
        <p>Selected guests may receive a private preview of what YouHodler is building for businesses. Full details will be shared only when approved.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
